Account-Based Marketing at Scale

Account-based marketing has long been recognized as the most effective strategy for targeting high-value B2B accounts. However, traditional ABM was resource-intensive and difficult to scale beyond a small number of named accounts.

AI infrastructure has changed this equation entirely. AI-powered ABM platforms can now orchestrate personalized campaigns for thousands of target accounts simultaneously, dynamically adjusting content, timing, and channel mix based on real-time engagement data.

